resources.string: Thola izaziso uma kwenzeke wahlangabezana nomuntu one-COVID-19.
Izimvume ezidingekayo ukufaka nokusebenzisa ngokugcwele lolu hlelo lokusebenza
Ukuqhubeka kwezimvume ezidingekayo ukufaka nokusebenzisa ngokugcwele lolu hlelo lokusebenza

Vula Izaziso Zokuhlangabezana kuze i-%1$s ingakwazisa uma bewuseduzane nomuntu obike ukuthi une-COVID-19. 

Ifoni yakho isebenzisa i-Bluetooth ukuze iqoqe futhi yabelane ngokuphephile ngama-ID angahleliwe namanye amafoni aseduzane. 

Idethi, ubude besikhathi, namandla esignali ahlobene nokudaluleka kuzokwabiwa nohlelo lokusebenza.
Siza ukwenza lolu hlelo lokusebenza lube ngcono
Yabelana ngedatha yokusetshenziswa kohlelo neyokusebenza ne-Google
Ukusiza ukugcina nokuthuthukisa uhlelo lokusebenza, enye idatha ehlonziwe enomkhawulo emayelana nokusebenza kohlelo lokusebenza nokusetshenziswa yabiwa ne-Google. Le datha ayikuhlonzi. %1$s
Kuze kube yilapho Izaziso Zokuhlangabezana zivuliwe, ngeke wazise ngokuhlangabezana okungase kube khona kwe-COVID-19
Uhlelo lwakho lokusebenza luhlala luhlola ukuhlangabezana okungaba khona.
Okwamanje abukho ubungozi bokuhlangabezana ne-COVID-19 obubikiwe ngawe. Uzokwaziswa lapho othile okade useduze naye ebika umphumela wokuhlolwa wokuba ne-COVID-19.
Irekhodi lokungena kwakamuva kokuhlangabezana okungaba khona
Imibiko yokuhlangabezana igcinwa izinsuku eziyi-14 kusuka kudethi yokuhlangabezana okungase kube khona.
Vikela umphakathi wakho, yabelana ngomphumela wakho wokuhlolwa we-COVID-19

Ukwabelana ngomphumela wakho wokuhlolwa we-COVID-19, ikakhulukazi lapho unaso isifo, kusozisa ukwazisa abanye okungenzeka baye bahlangabezana. Kuzokwazisa abanye emphakathini wakho ukuthi baqaphe izimpawu.
Uhlelo lwakho lokusebenza okwamanje aluhloli ukuhlangabezana okungaba khona. Ukuze waziswe ngokuhlangabezana ne-COVID-19 okungase kube khona, vula Izaziso Zokuhlangabezana.
Ungasiza abanye ngokuveza imiphumela ngokushesha. Nokho, ulwazi lomphumela wokuhlolwa olufakile kuze kube manje lulondolozwa kuhlelo lokusebenza ukuze uqhubeke nokuhlela ngemuva kwesikhathi.
Le khodi yesikhathi esisodwa isetshenziselwa ukuqinisekisa umphumela wakho wokuhlolwa futhi ayikwazi ukusetshenziswa futhi.
Kusiza uhlelo lokusebenza luthole ukuthi uthole nini isifo nokwazisa abantu abafanele ngokuhlangabezana okungase kube khona.
Ingabe uye wahamba ezinsukwini eziyi-14 ezedlule?

Siyabonga ngokwabelena ngesimo sakho se-COVID-19 nokusiza umphakathi wakho uhlale uphephile
Isimo sakho se-COVID-19 asizange sabiwe kodwa silondoloziwe kuhlelo lokusebenza. Ungase wabelane noma ususe isimo sakho noma kunini.
Imininingwane yomphumela wakho wokuhlolwa izosuswa kulolu hlelo lokusebenza.
Ayikwazi ukwabelana ngemiphumela yokuhlolwa kungaxhunyiwe kwi-inthanethi. Hlola ukuxhumeka kwakho kwe-inthanethi uphinde uzame futhi.
